President Cyril Ramaphosa and his Ugandan counterpart, President Yoweri Kaguta Museveni address the second day of the Business Forum at the Gallagher Convention Centre.  JOHANNESBURG - President Cyril Ramaphosa and his Ugandan counterpart, President Yoweri Kaguta Museveni will participate in a Business Forum, which started on Tuesday. Both presidents address the second day of the Business Forum at the Gallagher Convention Centre. Watch the event live in the video above.